values: 2 years later heyyyyyy. I forgot about this thing. whats everyone up to?? (if anyone still uses these things...)

The tides have changed and so have I. Which is why I'm going to abandon this journal. I never update anyway. And some things are better kept unsaid. Heather and I got an apartment. If you're someone I like, then you have my cell phone #. Feel free to use it. Peace out.
